{"id":"5e9c30459b6559241525db26","title":"Artist Profile: Sandro Kopp","content":"\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 11%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-2' class='gallery galleryid-8625 gallery-columns-9 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\tMissing Attachment\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\tMissing Attachment\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\tMissing Attachment\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\tMissing Attachment\n\t\t\t</dt></dl>\n\t\t\t<br style='clear: both' />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>This year’s <a href=\"https://www.</p><p>liberatum.org.uk/istancool-2011/\">Istancool Festival</a> opened with an exhibition entitled ‘<em>Being With You’, </em>a series of paintings by <strong>Sandro Kopp</strong>, painted over Skype, featuring volunteers who sat for the artist. The results are honest, introspective portraits that capture the digital means of creation in a rather subtle way. At first the work seems simply stylized, however beneath is a rather expertly crafted representation of the limitations of the digital form. The paintings have a way of filling in the blanks in a way that pixels demand, while portraying the subjects like a snap shot. In a strange way we’re seeing them in real time.</p>\n","slug":"8625-artist-feature-sandro-kopp","category":"arts","date":1308324916000,"wpid":8625,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":650,"height":650,"src":"2011/06/skype1use.jpg","placeholder":"data:image/jpeg;base64, "},"createdAt":1587294277286,"updatedAt":1588403553900,"author":"5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d24","old_image":"2011/06/skype1use.jpg","categories":["arts"]}